Hi everyone,

I would like to introduce you to MXroute. MXroute provides e-mail hosting for your domain. Although we accomodate clients of all types, we cater most to people who already understand how e-mail works. Our goals are simple:

- Budget prices
- Premium quality
- Reasonable support

We take a business model that we know works for the rest of the hosting industry and apply it to e-mail hosting. E-mail hosting is a market that is all too often known for high prices, low resources. Despite being subject to the same market conditions as the VPS market, it is still often over priced.

So what's the catch? Your support requests may take up to 24 hours to receive a response. If there is a service outage, this is not relevant. These will receive instant action, though resolutions are not always instant. Basically I expect you to know how to setup Outlook, but if you don't I will help you, and that help may not be instant.

We make no illusions about our service. We know that companies charge a lot more and offer a lot less uptime and redundancy. We provide a premium service by the following:

- DDOS protection
- Redunant front end routing points
- Secondary relay to hold incoming mail in the event of outage
- RAID10 storage with daily off-site backups

Now for the offers. I have a promo code for you below:

